<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT66">
<l>iṭamāva teṉṉeñca miṉṟellām paṇṭu</l>
<l>paṭaṉā kaṇaiṉeṭiya māṟku tiṭamāka</l>
<l>vaiyēṉ maticūṭi taṉṉō ṭayaṉaiṉāṉ</l>
<l>vaiyēṉāṭ ceyyēṉ valam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[From] today onwards, my heart is the abode of</l>
<l>the tall Māl who once [lay in] the bed that is the hooded serpent.</l>
<l>I, who am sharp, shall not consider the moon-bearer [Śiva] along with Aja-Brahmā</l>
<l>as true [gods]; I shall not serve [them] [thanks to God’s] might.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
